edu.stanford.nlp.sentiment

Class SentimentUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.nlp.sentiment.SentimentUtils

  • public class SentimentUtils
extends Object
    In the Sentiment dataset converted to tree form, the labels on the intermediate nodes are the sentiment scores and the leaves are the text of the sentence. This class provides routines to read a file of those trees and attach the sentiment score as the GoldLabel annotation.
    Author:
    John Bauer
